<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333333;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            margin: 30px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            max-width: 600px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .header {
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-align: center;
           background-color: #004085; 
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px;
            color: #333333;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #ffffff;
            background-color: #004085;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #777777;
        }
        .highlight {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #004085;
        }
        .logo {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .logo img {
            max-width: 150px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Welcome to the {!Community_Name}</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">          
            <p>Dear <span class="highlight">{!Receiving_User.FirstName}</span>,</p>
            <p>Thank you for joining our {!Community_Name}. Our community is dedicated to providing you with the assistance and resources you need.</p>
            <p>To get started, please visit the following link:</p>
            <p><a href="{!Community_Url}" class="button">Access the Portal</a></p>
            <p>Your username is: <span class="highlight">{!Receiving_User.Username}</span></p>
            <p>If you have any questions or require further assistance, do not hesitate to contact us.</p>
            <p>Best regards,</p>
            <p>{!Organization.Name}</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; {!Year} {!Organization.Name}. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>